- (sighs)

13:22.762 --> 13:24.395
Not exactly, but he had it coming.

13:24.397 --> 13:26.931
(sighs) You see, Detective,

13:26.933 --> 13:30.207
it turns out, he may actually
be my father after all.

13:30.210 --> 13:33.712
You've decided that the lead
suspect in this investigation

13:33.715 --> 13:35.081
may be your father?

13:35.084 --> 13:37.588
I know that God Johnson
is not the killer.

13:37.591 --> 13:38.691
And you know that because...

13:38.693 --> 13:39.744
Because another patient

13:39.746 --> 13:41.145
